## A boilerplate for react projects

Have features

* Hot reloading
* Use webpack server
* eslint with react presets
* Use of index.html as a template for auto generated html
* Everything is dynamically generated in the dist folder
* babelrc config

To use

```
npm install
npm start
```

* npm version - 6.14.4
* node version - v12.16.2
* react - 16.13.1
